<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P><EM>You've reached</EM><B><CODE> /construction</CODE></B><EM> , a =
portion=20
  of&nbsp; the Group34 team-project&nbsp; site that carries information =
and=20
  materials related to the construction and organization of the site =
itself as a=20
  web site.</EM></P>
  <P><EM>You are welcome to explore this and other =
construction-information=20
  pages. &nbsp; You'll need your hard hat and safety shoes.&nbsp; Right =
now, the=20
  scaffolding is just being erected, so you will have to watch out for =
drop-offs=20
  (broken links), wet concrete, and falling girders.</EM></P>
  <P><EM>If you'd rather find out about Group34 and the Group34 team =
project, go=20
  directly to the </EM><A=20
  =
href=3D"http://student.kitcampus.com/projects/group34/"><B><I>Group34</I>=
</B></A><EM>=20
  home page.&nbsp; If that doesn't work, return later.&nbsp; The content =
may be=20
  blocked off while the construction crew is working here.&nbsp; =
</EM></P>
  <P><EM>And if you are a member of Group34, you know how to find other =
material=20
  and work safely through the hazards.&nbsp; The secret word is spelled=20
  F-T-P.</EM></P>
  <HR color=3D#990033>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
